{"tid":657337,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"港人住屋悲歌　豬欄劏房50平方呎月租$2500細過囚室","createTime":"2018-05-08T04:13:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-08T05:11:07.000Z","uid":150685,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"afff8bf539c2bd77bfca019aa58765e182eb3edc","tid":657337,"uid":150685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T04:13:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2065000/2067501/hse_thumb_20180507_c_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2065000%2F2067501%2Fhse_thumb_20180507_c_1024.jpg&h=8e047753&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n劏房環境惡劣，但原來市區劏房已算好，更差的是新界區近年愈來愈多由豬欄、雞舍等改建而成的劏房，又指寮屋劏房人均居住面積僅63方呎，比獨立囚室更細。團體期望政府加快興建公屋，為市民盡解決住屋問題。<br />\n<br />\n鄰舍層面社區發展聯席去年10月至今年3月期間，透過面談方式訪問北區、大埔、元朗、屯門、荃灣、觀塘6個地區，共97戶居於寮屋區的劏房、貨櫃屋及組合屋的租戶，當中約8成為寮屋劏房住戶。<br />\n<br />\n調查發現，超過7成住戶居住面積不足200平方呎的單位，當中寮屋劏房租戶情況更嚴峻。在受訪的77名寮屋劏房戶中，各有4成的居住面積不足100平方呎及在101至200平方呎之間，中位數每戶則為150平方呎。<br />\n<br />\n聯席亦按照住戶情況，計算出寮屋劏房的人均居住面積僅有63平方呎，比面積有75平方呎的懲教署獨立囚室更細。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2065000/2067501/IMG_20180503_132429_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2065000%2F2067501%2FIMG_20180503_132429_1024.jpg&h=b1459eeb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n另外，逾半受訪住戶指「環境衞生」需要改善，如經常出現垃圾站爆滿、動物糞便缺乏清理等情況；約4成指有「漏水、滲水、水浸」問題；逾3成人則指有「屋內環境/空間」問題，如欠缺防火配套等。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">雖然寮屋劏房環境惡劣，但仍有價有市。近半受訪戶月租超過$3,500，當中寮屋劏房月租中位數為$2,800，比全港家庭的月租中位數$2,180高出逾2成，亦比公屋的月租中位數$1,500高出8成。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2067501/%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BD%8F%E5%B1%8B%E6%82%B2%E6%AD%8C%E3%80%80%E8%B1%AC%E6%AC%84%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF50%E5%B9%B3%E6%96%B9%E5%91%8E%E6%9C%88%E7%A7%9F-2500%E7%B4%B0%E9%81%8E%E5%9B%9A%E5%AE%A4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2067501%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E4%25BD%258F%25E5%25B1%258B%25E6%2582%25B2%25E6%25AD%258C%25E3%2580%2580%25E8%25B1%25AC%25E6%25AC%2584%25E5%258A%258F%25E6%2588%25BF50%25E5%25B9%25B3%25E6%2596%25B9%25E5%2591%258E%25E6%259C%2588%25E7%25A7%259F-2500%25E7%25B4%25B0%25E9%2581%258E%25E5%259B%259A%25E5%25AE%25A4&d=Qp6g70ogGxeTF%2Bo8yHqdF3adZns4eLIrfSaUqUvMaEw%3D&h=db63733e\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2067501/%E6%B8%AF%E4%BA%BA%E4%BD%8F%E5%B1%8B%E6%82%B2%E6%AD%8C%E3%80%80%E8%B1%AC%E6%AC%84%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF50%E5%B9%B3%E6%96%B9%E5%91%8E%E6%9C%88%E7%A7%9F-2500%E7%B4%B0%E9%81%8E%E5%9B%9A%E5%AE%A4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 痴撚線咁都月租2500"},{"pid":"e8a3f85513f64ca2cb97aee21a97ea8e9f72d3f8","tid":657337,"uid":61280,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T04:26:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">又係HKET呢D突然扮持平突然關心弱勢既狗媒！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各港豬小心一大乍涼粉狗媒（包括CC台綾波麗幾隻狗5毛！！)趁大便論時間既土地問題SPIN大合唱！！！！！</span></span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"385c0303d962ccac1f5c8f0c7dc0bdec43a5fc3b","tid":657337,"uid":93266,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T04:30:27.000Z","msg":"都係自己揀<br />\n<br />\n講真<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我寧願訓街算啦"},{"pid":"e1ac83acd77dac91e130508616dd5a9aaa95ca52","tid":657337,"uid":120715,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T04:53:04.000Z","msg":"冇屋住最住住宿地方係囚室<br />\n又可以用政府錢, 又有屋住, 唔怕有漏水, 最多悶少少同可能俾人打"},{"pid":"13c385d7aa98eb7a485c94a35a1bf7e5a6be5130","tid":657337,"uid":6752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-08T05:02:20.000Z","msg":"香港真係自由<br />\n天橋,天橋底,路邊,豬欄都住得"},{"pid":"1c866576b41528f3a818d2a303a0c6f